cs.DL, cs.CY, cs.IR, cs.CR, cs.SI 

The paper focuses on Open Access integration at the institutional level, which is related to digital libraries (cs.DL) and cyberinfrastructure (cs.CY). The use of Unpaywall and Leiden Ranking suggests a focus on information retrieval (cs.IR) and data analysis (cs.CR). Finally, the exploration of differences between and within countries and the general ranking of universities could also be related to social and information networks (cs.SI).
